data.description: Nestled in the heart of vibrant entertainment and delectable dining options, this recent remodel awaits your arrival. Step into a big open kitchen boasting elegant granite countertops, sleek stainless steel appliances, and the convenience of soft-close drawers. Retreat to the master suite featuring a spacious walk-in closet and a luxurious dual sink vanity, offering the epitome of relaxation and comfort. Outside, a fenced yard provides the perfect space for outdoor gatherings, while a detached garage ensures ample parking and storage options. Don't miss your chance to call this home yours!
